descriptions.content: Fitness Canada Physio and Massage Centre is a proudly Canadian health care company, owned by a Physiotherapist. We provide diversified Therapy services across the City of Calgary. At our clinics our Physiotherapists, Massage Therapists, Yoga therapists, Acupuncturists and Therapy Assistants work in a team to help our patients understand their conditions and work along with the team to realize their therapeutic goals.

Our unique specialty is our Holistic approach-by which we mean collaboration of Modern advanced Therapeutic Modalities with the Ancient Wisdom like Yoga and Ayurveda ( Indian -Herbal Therapy) to assist our patients achieve Long lasting Goals at a shortest period of time.

Our Therapists have extensive Training and experience in their field of expertise. With all those expertise, our therapists are enabled to treat a variety of conditions like: Musculo Skeletal problems, Sports Injuries, Motor Vehicle Accidents, TMJ-Issues, Vestibular Rehabilitation, Work related Injuries(WCB),Chronic Pain syndromes.
As a Valuable customer, you can always discuss to our therapists and make a well informed decision about your health goals. To us : You-the Patient is our Lead Team member.

We currently have three locations across NW, SW and South Calgary. As a fastly growing company we are looking forward to expand our services to other part of the City to provide the same excellent care to people from across the city.
We appreciate your interest in Fitness Canada Physio and Massage Centre, and invite you to take the leap to collaborate with us to take your Health and Fitness to the next level.
Physiotherapy uses a range of non-invasive treatment techniques and has applications in almost all disciplines of modern medicine.
